a lot of devotion,

292
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:28,190
let's observe Sunday.

293
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:30,789
Sure. I'm a devout Catholic.

294
00:17:30,789 --> 00:17:31,789
Don't worry.

295
00:17:33,289 --> 00:17:37,130
Please don't eat bread during
a mass. I'm so embarrassed.

296
00:17:37,359 --> 00:17:39,460
I ate it as I couldn't hear well.

297
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,559
Why are you saying that?

298
00:17:40,559 --> 00:17:42,900
Then if you eat a lot of food,

299
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:45,400
can you hear something
from far away?

300
00:17:45,470 --> 00:17:46,799
