301
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:48,509
I guess...

302
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,740
I have supernatural power.

303
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:54,079
Don't be ridiculous.

304
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:56,980
It's true. Stay here and tell me.

305
00:17:57,779 --> 00:18:00,250
Go ahead. Song Sac, say something.

306
00:18:00,279 --> 00:18:01,349
Say something now.

307
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:03,450
Say it.

308
00:18:03,619 --> 00:18:06,519
Peter Piper picked a pack of
pickled peppers.

309
00:18:06,619 --> 00:18:08,289
