310
00:18:08,730 --> 00:18:10,259
I said it, you pig.

311
00:18:10,990 --> 00:18:14,000
Where did you learn such a word?

312
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:15,200
I'm sorry.

313
00:18:16,670 --> 00:18:18,140
