316
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,400
It's your new mass clothes.

317
00:19:22,869 --> 00:19:24,200
I can wear what I have now.

318
00:19:24,470 --> 00:19:26,970
It looked small as I saw it
at the last mass.

319
00:19:27,539 --> 00:19:28,539
Thank you.

320
00:19:29,210 --> 00:19:31,009
- Father Kim.
- Yes.

321
00:19:32,039 --> 00:19:33,910
If there are much fewer people
at church this week...

322
00:19:35,579 --> 00:19:37,509
although I'm preparing my heart...

323
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:41,319
The number of people who visit
the church is nothing, but...

324
00:19:42,589 --> 00:19:43,690
Let's just do it.

325
00:19:45,220 --> 00:19:47,319
If someone comes to church
trusting Father Lee,

326
00:19:48,789 --> 00:19:50,990
I should hold a mass
even for just one person.

327
00:19:52,299 --> 00:19:53,359
Yes, Father Kim.

328
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:55,900
Let's keep the church,

329
00:19:58,569 --> 00:20:00,470
recover Father Lee's honor,

330
00:20:03,509 --> 00:20:05,039
and correct the wrongs.

331
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:07,210
Yes.

332
00:20:14,150 --> 00:20:16,690
I never imagined there would be
such a few people.

333
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:20,119
It might get better after two weeks.

334
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:23,190
If it goes like this...

335
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:27,460
Our church wouldn't be
one without a priest, right?

336
00:20:28,769 --> 00:20:30,170
That won't happen.

337
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:33,000
Here they are.

338
00:20:34,170 --> 00:20:35,369
- Hello.
- Hello.

339
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:38,009
- Hello, Father.
- Hello.

340
00:20:38,339 --> 00:20:39,410
Did you eat bread?

341
00:20:39,809 --> 00:20:41,309
Yes, I ate it before I came here.

342
00:20:41,579 --> 00:20:42,880
Flick a crumb off of your mouth.

343
00:20:47,650 --> 00:20:48,690
Hello.

344
00:20:50,319 --> 00:20:52,759
- Hello, Father.
- Hello.

345
00:21:06,740 --> 00:21:08,269
Are you going to come in or not?

346
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:13,609
If you're going to stay here,
go home and watch "Animal Farm".

347
00:21:13,779 --> 00:21:16,009
Well, we were being considerate
to come here.

348
00:21:16,009 --> 00:21:18,079
You shouldn't say so.

349
00:21:18,079 --> 00:21:20,819
It's not easy for us to come in.

350
00:21:20,819 --> 00:21:22,190
Staying here means...

351
00:21:22,190 --> 00:21:23,750
