Father Lee did a bad thing.

352
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:26,089
I don't want to hold mass for people
who have such thoughts.

353
00:21:26,390 --> 00:21:28,630
You need to apologize to us.

354
00:21:28,630 --> 00:21:29,960
How come you blame us?

355
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,500
What do I have to apologize?

356
00:21:31,559 --> 00:21:32,660
Father.

357
00:21:32,829 --> 00:21:34,500
You believe easily, judge easily,

358
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:36,269
and get swept off easily.

359
00:21:36,630 --> 00:21:37,930
You don't deserve to believe in God.

360
00:21:37,930 --> 00:21:39,440
You don't have to come to church.
Go back.

361
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:40,900
I'm really appalled.

362
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:43,569
