these days...

365
00:21:49,180 --> 00:21:50,380
Fine.

366
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:51,880
Let's go.

367
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:53,079
You know...

368
00:21:53,319 --> 00:21:55,119
Catarina, Catarina.

369
00:21:55,119 --> 00:21:56,490
Wait a minute!

370
00:22:00,319 --> 00:22:01,319
How...

371
00:22:01,990 --> 00:22:04,829
How can you do this?

372
00:22:04,829 --> 00:22:07,759
Not so many people
come to church anyway.

373
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,500
Excuse me...

374
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,700
Father!

375
00:22:14,440 --> 00:22:15,509
Father!

376
00:22:21,279 --> 00:22:23,480
It's troublesome to go to
another church.

377
00:22:25,720 --> 00:22:27,849
It might be embarrassing
if I just go inside.

378
00:23:21,910 --> 00:23:23,710
I told you not to come
to our church, old man.

379
00:23:30,650 --> 00:23:33,279
I'm the one who decides
to come here or not.

380
00:23:33,450 --> 00:23:35,819
I told you that you're
not qualified to come here.

381
00:23:35,890 --> 00:23:37,789
Did you think I wouldn't come...

382
00:23:37,789 --> 00:23:38,859
as I worry,
"He says I'm not qualified."

383
00:23:39,859 --> 00:23:41,789
I don't want you to listen to
my sermon.

384
00:23:41,789 --> 00:23:43,390
