- What?

390
00:23:52,799 --> 00:23:55,210
You shouldn't go too far.

391
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:58,279
Do you get an allergic reaction
if you don't get in trouble?

392
00:23:58,509 --> 00:24:00,180
Does it prevent the descent of
the Holy Ghost?

393
00:24:01,549 --> 00:24:03,210
I guess you heard about Mr. Hwang's
awarding ceremony.

394
00:24:03,210 --> 00:24:06,049
Yes, I did. So please keep quiet.

395
00:24:06,049 --> 00:24:07,880
How many times
do I have to tell you?

396
00:24:08,289 --> 00:24:11,990
I'm currently losing, but I'll soon
catch up and turn the tables.

397
00:24:12,390 --> 00:24:13,619
It's driving me crazy.

398
00:24:15,660 --> 00:24:17,289
Do you know why I'm not sending
you to prison...

399
00:24:17,289 --> 00:24:18,500
