400
00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:22,670
It's how I express my last respect
to Father Lee.

401
00:24:23,630 --> 00:24:26,440
Regardless of the crime,
I thought him as a saint once.

402
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:28,769
It's how I show my respect.
Do you understand?

403
00:24:29,539 --> 00:24:30,569
However,

404
00:24:30,769 --> 00:24:32,539
my respect has a limit.

405
00:24:32,839 --> 00:24:34,240
So you need to realize
the situation.

406
00:24:34,950 --> 00:24:36,910
I'll go as far as I can go.

407
00:24:37,150 --> 00:24:39,549
- So tell them to be prepared.
- Do as you like.

408
00:24:40,150 --> 00:24:42,119
You can go to National Assembly
or the Blue House.

409
00:24:42,890 --> 00:24:46,259
