439
00:26:05,839 --> 00:26:09,609
Darn it. I should rip
that priest's lips.

440
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:11,339
Don't get upset.

441
00:26:13,440 --> 00:26:14,740
Find a replacement.

442
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:18,319
Pick a religious group.
